to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Daily Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — daily at 8:00. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"bea880fa-f4a8-6ad4-67e0-a90e4680d97f","name":"Note: Daily Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fetch Changes (Google Sheets) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"b19ab51b-f7f8-ffaf-a2ef-73493e2dee60","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Changes (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Normalize Records · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"6285f967-b205-4d12-c5c3-198ea9f93f00","name":"Note: Fetch Changes (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Normalize Records\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming job records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Upsert into Google Sheets","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"75c2d0a6-a5a5-7ea4-14bc-b1bbeb9220fa","name":"Note: Normalize Records"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Advance Watermark · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"cbe97b61-8b8b-9500-09e7-47e2e0896404","name":"Note: Upsert into Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Advance Watermark\n\nCustom JavaScript: Advance the incremental watermark to the newest record seen\n\nNext: Persist Watermark (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"7133567c-742f-c501-e222-de57c4720819","name":"Note: Advance Watermark"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Watermark (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Save Execution Metadata · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"39bf3177-3f74-1333-87b9-e7ec8cdd4af7","name":"Note: Persist Watermark (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"11489374-e6da-89eb-d86d-6361ea9c6581","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Sort Jobs Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"93f2c53a-e558-2748-0b39-a90a12125731","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Jobs Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty type","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"cff30446-6e33-b111-8a30-ca3c24124090","name":"Note: Sort Jobs Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty type\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"4b084fdb-3111-66a8-e8d2-43d641203721","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"0d8fddf5-ea30-693e-ee84-880e48fbf4fb","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"a1965a29-62ce-8cb6-bff6-edb3540badf7","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"01f69386-89c1-e39e-8e0b-582bf30f9889","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"95695c60-55a7-af6d-4c9a-2c4eae491080","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"c6b09c54-968b-18ec-ba10-69f8a46de851","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"5f125916-6d0b-de6d-3993-8c0dcd3b695d","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,1540],"id":"b8f118d2-a8d3-259d-adf2-d77b95ef19d0","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,1540],"id":"371f2d25-22f4-252c-44df-413e323584f3","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Sync records between tools with HubSpot and Google Sheets without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Two-System Sync · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nSync records between tools with HubSpot and Google Sheets without manual work. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual process orchestration is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Load Previous Snapshot → Fetch Changes (Google Sheets) → Normalize Records → Upsert into Google Sheets → Advance Watermark → Persist Watermark (HubSpot) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to two-system sync without manual effort\n- Anyone automating process orchestration in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"39a97c68-3687-f86d-6025-b14fe6d50bbc","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"d207ea8d-53be-7715-7889-5b6f1f2dae7c","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your process orchestration process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"f6c22d6d-ecb4-f354-e41d-2be875f87938","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fetch Changes (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Changes (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Records","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Records":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert into Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert into Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Advance Watermark","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Advance Watermark":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Watermark (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Watermark (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Jobs Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Jobs Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty type":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"88591f94-4388-4566-9715-d8cf80942b56","id":"FDX06218"}